document_data.Notable Users:
* The [[Glow Shoppe]], a store in [[Ravens Bluff]] that sold various light sources, kept candle molds in its backroom so that [[Sul Loman]] could make the tallow and wax candles they sold.{{Cite polyhedron/48/The Living City: The Glow Shop|28}}
* [[Gulmarin Reldacap]], Lord High Smith and Artificer of the [[House of Gond]] in [[Essembra]], was a brilliant inventor who made advancements in candle mold designs.<ref>
* The [[Sharran]]s of [[Vanrakdoom]] used candle molds to create the black wax candles they used all throughout the temple.
